text: Wangen bei Olten is a municipality in the district Olten in the canton of Solothurn in Switzerland. == Demographics == As of December 2020, Wangen bei Olten has a population of 5239 people. Most of the people speak German there. == Education == Wangen bei Olten has 1 Secondary school and 3 Primary schools. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Olten District
